<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to RSOLV Early Access Program</title>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap');

    body {
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
    }
    .container {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 30px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    }
    .logo {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .logo img {
      max-width: 200px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #10b981;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 24px;
    }
    h1, h2, h3 {
      color: #10b981;
    }
    p {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .section {
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .steps {
      background-color: #f3f4f6;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .step {
      display: flex;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .step-number {
      background-color: #10b981;
      color: white;
      width: 30px;
      height: 30px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-right: 15px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .step-content {
      flex-grow: 1;
    }
    .cta {
      background-color: #10b981;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      display: inline-block;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-top: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .benefits {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 15px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .benefit {
      background-color: #f3f4f6;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      border-left: 3px solid #10b981;
    }
    .benefit h3 {
      margin-top: 0;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 40px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b7280;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      padding-top: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .social {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 15px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .social a {
      color: #6b7280;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .benefits {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="logo">
      <img src="https://rsolv.dev/images/rsolv_logo_transparent.png" alt="RSOLV Logo">
    </div>

    <div class="header">
      <h1>Welcome to the RSOLV Early Access Program!</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <p>Hi <%= @first_name %>,</p>

      <p>Thank you for joining the RSOLV Early Access Program! We're thrilled to have you on board as one of our first users to experience our proactive security scanning and automated remediation platform.</p>

      <p>You're now part of an exclusive group that will help shape the future of automated security. RSOLV continuously scans your repositories for vulnerabilities and generates fixes automatically. You only pay for fixes that actually make it into your codebase - no commitments, just results.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>Getting Started</h2>

      <div class="steps">
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">1</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Connect Your Repositories</h3>
            <p>Visit your dashboard to enable RSOLV for the repositories you want to scan. RSOLV will immediately begin analyzing your code for security vulnerabilities.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">2</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Add Our GitHub Action</h3>
            <p>Install our GitHub Action to enable automated fix generation. Add your <code>RSOLV_API_KEY</code> as a repository secret.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">3</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Review & Fix Vulnerabilities</h3>
            <p>RSOLV will create issues for vulnerabilities found. Tag any issue with <code>rsolv:automate</code> to generate a secure pull request automatically.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <a href="https://rsolv.dev/docs/getting-started" class="cta">View Setup Instructions</a>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>Early Access Benefits</h2>

      <div class="benefits">
        <div class="benefit">
          <h3>üöÄ Priority Support</h3>
          <p>Get personalized support directly from our engineering team.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="benefit">
          <h3>üí° Shape the Product</h3>
          <p>Your feedback will directly influence our development roadmap.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="benefit">
          <h3>üéÅ 10 Free Fixes</h3>
          <p>Your first 10 fixes are free. Only pay for fixes you deploy after that.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="benefit">
          <h3>‚≠ê Founding Member Status</h3>
          <p>Exclusive benefits when we launch publicly.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>What's Coming Up</h2>
      <p>Over the next few days, you'll receive a series of emails with tips and best practices to help you get the most out of RSOLV. Here's what to expect:</p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Day 1:</strong> Understanding your security scan results</li>
        <li><strong>Day 3:</strong> How to prioritize and fix vulnerabilities</li>
        <li><strong>Day 7:</strong> Advanced security features and best practices</li>
      </ul>

      <p>If you have any questions or need assistance at any point, just reply to this email and our team will help you out!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <p>We're excited to have you on this journey with us!</p>

      <p>Best regards,<br>The RSOLV Team</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <div class="social">
        <a href="https://twitter.com/rsolvai">Twitter</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/rsolv-ai">GitHub</a>
        <a href="https://rsolv.dev/blog">Blog</a>
      </div>

      <p>This email was sent to <%= @email %>. If you did not sign up for RSOLV, please disregard this email.</p>
      <p>&copy; 2025 RSOLV - Proactive Security Scanning & Automated Remediation. Pay Only for Fixes You Deploy.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>